Salmonellosis, orange juice - USA (Northwest) 990628213324
Salmonellosis, orange juice - USA (Northwest) (02) 990630162221
Salmonellosis, orange juice - USA (Northwest) (03) 990701103008
Salmonellosis, orange juice - USA (Northwest) (04) 990701233925
Date: Wed, 7 Jul 1999 08:45:31 -0300
From: Dick Hamilton <rhamilto@direct.ca>
Source: Vancouver Sun [edited
For the record, the [local newspaper reported July 1,1999 that orange
juice from Sun Orchards Inc., Tempe, AZ was distributed to restaurants and
other commercial food service establishments in British Columbia and
Alberta. It is not sold in retail food outlets.
Four people in British Columbia were affected following consumption of the
juice.
